    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portable, removable computer drives that operate via a type of non-volatile flash memory in which data can be written or erased only in blocks, and that connect to a computer via USB port.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
